------------------------------------Post----------------------------------------------
1. Add Customer : Method "Post"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customer/add
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
   {
    
    "userName" : "rameshs",
     "pass" : "ramesh06",
    "email" : "ramesh6gmail.com",
    "firstName":"ram6",
    "lastName": "Kumar6"
	}
	
------------------------------------GET----------------------------------------------
1. Get Customer By Id : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customer/get/7

1. Get All Customers : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customer/getAll

------------------------------------UPDATE----------------------------------------------

1. Update Customer : Method "PUT"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customer/updateCustomer/8
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
    {
    "iD": 8,
    "userName" : "rameshs",
     "pass" : "ramesh08",
    "email" : "ramesh8gmail.com",
    "firstName":"ram8",
    "lastName": "Kumar6"
   
  }
	
------------------------------------DELETE----------------------------------------------
1. Delete Customer : Method "DELETE"
2. URL:	http://localhost:9092/customer/delete/8
	